g.text: 7.6 per cent of unemployed Victorians had been unemployed for 2 years or more as at March 2021
Source: ABS Labour Force, Detailed (monthly). Note: most recent data is for March 2021. Data not seasonally adjusted. Smoothed using a 3 month rolling average.
